  cat <<'EOF'
model_id|display_name|family|modality|use_case|runtime|size_class|minimum_vram_gb|minimum_ram_gb|cpu_ok|gpu_preferred|install_method|verify_command|enabled_by_default|notes
gemma3-4b|Gemma 3 4B|Gemma|text|coding|ollama|small|0|8|true|false|ollama pull gemma3:4b|ollama run gemma3:4b -- "hello"|true|Fast local general-purpose model
gemma3-12b|Gemma 3 12B|Gemma|text|reasoning|ollama|medium|8|16|true|true|ollama pull gemma3:12b|ollama run gemma3:12b -- "hello"|true|Stronger reasoning when RAM allows
qwen2.5-7b|Qwen2.5 7B|Qwen|text|infra_audit|ollama|medium|0|16|true|false|ollama pull qwen2.5:7b|ollama run qwen2.5:7b -- "hello"|true|Good all-around operator model
qwen2.5-coder-7b|Qwen2.5 Coder 7B|Qwen|text|coding|ollama|medium|0|16|true|false|ollama pull qwen2.5-coder:7b|ollama run qwen2.5-coder:7b -- "hello"|true|Code-focused local model
llama3.1-8b|Llama 3.1 8B|Llama|text|planning|ollama|medium|0|16|true|false|ollama pull llama3.1:8b|ollama run llama3.1:8b -- "hello"|true|Open local planning candidate
bitnet-3b-experimental|BitNet 3B Experimental|BitNet|text|memory|local_binary|tiny|0|8|true|false|install from approved local package|bitnet --version|false|Experimental low-footprint text model
whisper-small|Whisper Small|Whisper|audio|speech_to_text|local_binary|small|0|4|true|false|install from approved local package|whisper --help|false|Optional audio transcription helper
